update $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data stpvd2
set rule_row_pass_fail_indicator = stpvd1.rule_row_pass_fail_indicator
from $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data stpvd1
where stpvd1.policy_number =stpvd2.policy_number
and stpvd1.policy_source_system_id = stpvd2.policy_source_system_id
and stpvd1.transaction_datetime = stpvd2.transaction_datetime
and stpvd1.rule_id = stpvd2.rule_id
and stpvd1.condition_order_number = 1
and stpvd2.condition_order_number = 2
and stpvd2.rule_row_pass_fail_indicator = 'NULL';

UPDATE $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data
SET overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator = (
    WITH status_cte AS (
        SELECT
            policy_source_system_id, transaction_datetime, rule_id,
            CASE
                WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN rule_row_pass_fail_indicator = 'FAIL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0 THEN 'FAIL'
                ELSE 'PASS'
            END AS computed_status
        FROM $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data sub
        WHERE sub.policy_source_system_id = $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data.policy_source_system_id
        AND sub.transaction_datetime = $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data.transaction_datetime
        AND sub.rule_id = $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data.rule_id
        GROUP BY policy_source_system_id, transaction_datetime, rule_id
    )
    SELECT computed_status FROM status_cte
);

UPDATE $$refined_schema.straight_through_processing_validated_data
SET stp_validated_data_loaded_to_api_table_status =
    CASE
        WHEN overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator = 'PASS' THEN 'STP - no action required'
        WHEN overall_rule_pass_fail_indicator = 'FAIL' THEN 'Load to API table pending'
        ELSE 'NULL'
    END;
